Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:30.78,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}赤夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  驅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能…這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結…花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠和那人相見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的風  真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正找你呢  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好你沒先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮？在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7年前  我的姐姐自殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於在孤兒院裡長大的我來說  她是唯一的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我無法接受現實  封閉了自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在同一個孤兒院出身的結花一直對我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身邊  給我笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有結花的話  我會變成怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.49,0:05:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香央里  匡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到驅同學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他在樓頂看月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直在樓頂單獨相處到現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底幹了些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼幹了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有點激動人心的展開嗎  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西要拍下來  拍下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在妄想什麼奇怪的東西啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  匡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香央里你做得太過火了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你讓我認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把真正的我喚醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒人能阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好強  你這傢伙難道是傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於和結花之外的人都不怎麼交流的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有香央里和匡會正常跟我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這開朗的兩人在一起  心情也自然舒暢起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,促銷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  「阿亞納斯」今天和明天有兩天清倉大減價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿亞納斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的清倉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多哦  服裝啊雜貨之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感的封面偶像寫真集之類的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  色匡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就過去  你們要不要也一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了  不想去擠人堆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  下次再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花在上小學的時候被這水奈瀨家領養了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有孩子的水奈瀨夫妻很溫柔地接納了結花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿亞納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅…驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的…月亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.93,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  這裡空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都消失到什麼地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來…了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做惡夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但為什麼  結花你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接你的時候  發現門是開著的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為發生了什麼事  挺著急的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天回來的時候  腦子一直不清醒  就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花你才是  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚一直沒合眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕閉上眼睛  非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一晚沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是睡著的麼  這麼香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是…就結果來說算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  紅色的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在親密無間地搞約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好保護的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會保護好結花的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  別再擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  別在這地方哭呀  會被人誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人家弄哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早就把女生給弄哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我要向大家介紹一位新同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百野栞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛  好萌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百野同學她是來自義大利的歸國子女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義大利？  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那百野同學  就請你做下自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平時都對些什麼感興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問題要按順序來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就先問下三圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你們不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還請你們不要干涉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  人家已經能自己走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過就是因為睡眠不足罷了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擋道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒長眼睛麼  這有病人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  扮公主嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不是  那個  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是貧血而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  那我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皐月…同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那隻眼睛怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想說就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水奈瀨…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君他的右眼看不見東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為這個原因吧  瞳孔的顏色也跟常人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就戴上了眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  你男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？老  老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  還停留在那種階段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  睡了一覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以已經沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  讓你擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體沒問題了的話  那我們就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿亞納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是沒去成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且清倉大減價到今天就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦  我爸媽說了  讓你偶爾也來我家吃頓飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回家的時候  要不要順路去一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  還是下回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都帶著這東西  到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  企藏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企藏…先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企藏先生它可厲害了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒  還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不買  真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟驅君你在一起  只是那樣看著就覺得挺開心的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然昨天的衝擊和不安還沒有消退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這副笑臉絕對是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也那樣  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那東西」到底是什麼  已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再讓結花受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要它不再出現  也就這麼算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安靜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能一直都這樣  該多好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  姐姐會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結花
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.37,0:24:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水晶的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.64,0:24:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在惡夢的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有答案嗎
